Independent Fortinet wire peer for sing-openconnect M3.

The authentication, XML configuration, response-less TLS switch, clthello and
svrhello application exchange, Fortinet framing, and pppd shim are independently
implemented from the observable wire contracts in OpenConnect commit
2035601b64a5360a46d18e08937e7f654b3230f2. The data plane is terminated by
Debian pppd 2.5.2-1+1. TLS uses Python's OpenSSL-backed ssl module; DTLS 1.2
uses the separately packaged OpenSSL s_server rather than the production Go
DTLS implementation.
